{"tid":799133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大美國商會：美加本周可能達成NAFTA協議","createTime":"2018-08-29T22:51:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T13:36:20.000Z","uid":141151,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"eee8dface33221246db209cd9a6693ba60c07dc3","tid":799133,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T22:51:05.000Z","msg":"《國際經濟》加拿大美國商會：美加本周可能達成NAFTA協議<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180829002270-260410\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20180829002270-260410&d=Zv7mRUQtUzp1GiUzrZYPeQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=013103bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180829002270-260410</a><br />\n<br />\nCNBC報導，加拿大美國商會（Canadian American Business Council,CABC）表示，加拿大本周可能與美國就修訂《北美自由貿易協定》（NAFTA）達成協議。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大周二正式與美國重啟貿易談判，盼能在未來幾天簽署協議。美國財長穆努欽（Steven Mnuchin）周二接受CNBC訪問時表示，美加兩國已經取得許多進展，美國希望加拿大能加入，但如果無法實現，美方將推進與墨西哥的協議。他預計美加貿易談判能在本周結束。<br />\n<br />\n此前美國總統川普揚言，若加拿大不加入修訂後的協議，美國將對加拿大生產的汽車實施關稅。<br />\n<br />\nCABC執行長格林伍德（Maryscott Greenwood）周二接受CNBC訪問時表示，她認為加拿大將加入協議，甚至可能在本周就完成修訂版NAFTA。她表示：「美加貿易協商剩下的難題不多，而墨西哥已經就位，我真的認為我們本周可以達成」。"},{"pid":"9d9b0d1faeb413157dac493693ba099ce2e5a5d9","tid":799133,"uid":997,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T23:24:02.000Z","msg":"條on9總理迫住入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7300b63c00b3fd23254045463a64316e8088c793","tid":799133,"uid":4239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T03:43:16.000Z","msg":"自組新WTO？"},{"pid":"78b2b3d3bbb3b433b2a2fecc2cbb0a99e455d7b3","tid":799133,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T15:19:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b32f731410d93e3bfd2e15d39f5a498f737e7ebf","tid":799133,"uid":121146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T15:21:51.000Z","msg":"左膠總理說好的反侵呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5558f5e576c41dade9c92810457d3bce772493dd","tid":799133,"uid":121146,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T15:30:38.000Z","msg":"加拿大歸邊後  已經係最大經濟體<br />\n歐洲實唔執輸話入  之後真係比侵侵對現到美國優先既承諾了<br />\n好難唔服佢  兩年內開十幾條戰線  全部係理想中結果"},{"pid":"8f80d130210e5257978420ef4010e61fc4c2a735","tid":799133,"uid":39855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5558f5e576c41dade9c92810457d3bce772493dd","tid":799133,"uid":121146,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T15:30:38.000Z","msg":"加拿大歸邊後  已經係最大經濟體<br />\n歐洲實唔執輸話入  之後真係比侵侵對現到美國優先既承諾了<br />\n好難唔服佢  兩年內開十幾條戰線  全部係理想中結果"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T15:39:25.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"a86bb8649d188bf733fc666e1959f4a1958216bd","tid":799133,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b32f731410d93e3bfd2e15d39f5a498f737e7ebf","tid":799133,"uid":121146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T15:21:51.000Z","msg":"左膠總理說好的反侵呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T15:45:23.000Z","msg":"唔係講笑，現在左膠好 high，因總理『甘』對侵侵說不<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b03039955bcf862adcb5e8ffa0740c216cf4b234","tid":799133,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5558f5e576c41dade9c92810457d3bce772493dd","tid":799133,"uid":121146,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T15:30:38.000Z","msg":"加拿大歸邊後  已經係最大經濟體<br />\n歐洲實唔執輸話入  之後真係比侵侵對現到美國優先既承諾了<br />\n好難唔服佢  兩年內開十幾條戰線  全部係理想中結果"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T15:50:18.000Z","msg":"唔係講笑，如果加拿大真係放棄奶業保護去歸邊，會係幾大新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/ass